decks.notes: This deck revolves around a powerful combo involving Thassa's Oracle and Paradigm Shift. The goal is to use Paradigm Shift to exile your entire library, then control Thassa's Oracle to win the game. The deck includes cards like Preordain, Impulse, and Thought Lash to help find the combo pieces and control the game. It also includes counter spells like Force of Will and Daze to protect the combo, and mana acceleration cards like Lotus Petal and Ancient Tomb to ramp up quickly. The deck overall aims to quickly assemble the combo and win the game in a single turn.
